OL,3,CConsumer confidence reaches highest
OL,4,Cpoint of year despite 'clouds on
OL,5,Chorizon'
OL,7,FConsumer confidence has reached its
OL,8,Fhighest point this year amid "clouds
OL,9,Fon the horizon" in the form of
OL,10,Finflation and rising unemployment,
OL,11,Faccording to a long-running survey.
OL,13,FGfK's Consumer Confidence Index
OL,14,Fincreased by two points to minus 17 in
OL,15,FAugust, driven by improved personal
OL,16,Ffinances likely thanks to the latest
OL,17,Fcut to interest rates.
OL,19,FEarlier this month, the Bank of
OL,20,FEngland voted to cut its base interest
OL,21,Frate from 4.25% to 4%.
