OL,7,FConfidence in personal finances over
OL,8,Fboth the last year and the coming 12
OL,9,Fmonths rose three points, to minus
OL,10,Ffour and positive five respectively.
OL,12,FThe measure for the general economic
OL,13,Fsituation of the country during the
OL,14,Flast 12 months is up two points to
OL,15,Fminus 42 ` seven points worse than a
OL,16,Fyear ago ` while the expectations for
OL,17,Fthe next 12 months fell one point to
OL,18,Fminus 30 ` 15 points worse than last
OL,19,FAugust.
