OL,3,CConsumer confidence reaches highest
OL,4,Cpoint of year despite 'clouds on
OL,5,Chorizon'
OL,7,FThe major purchase index ` a measure
OL,8,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,9,Fitems ` is up two points to minus 13.
OL,11,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,12,Fdirector at GfK, said: "The biggest
OL,13,Fchanges in August are in confidence in
OL,14,Fpersonal finances, with the scores
OL,15,Flooking back and ahead a year each up
OL,16,Fby three points.
OL,18,F"This is likely due to the Bank of
OL,19,FEngland's August 7 cut in interest
OL,20,Frates, delivering the lowest cost of
OL,21,Fborrowing for more than two years.
