OL,5,Chorizon'
OL,7,F"The improved sentiment on personal
OL,8,Ffinances is welcome, but there are
OL,9,Fmany clouds on the horizon in the form
OL,10,Fof inflation ` the highest since
OL,11,FJanuary 2024 ` and rising unemployment.
OL,13,F"There's no shortage of speculation,
OL,14,Ftoo, about what the autumn budget will
OL,15,Fbring in terms of tax rises."
