OL,7,FHe added: "While August's overall
OL,8,Findex score of minus 17 is the best
OL,9,Fthis year, consumer confidence
OL,10,Fcontinues to move in a very narrow
OL,11,Fband, and there's no sense that it is
OL,12,Fabout to break out into fresher, more
OL,13,Foptimistic territory.
OL,15,F"The UK's consumers are still in wait-
OL,16,Fand-see mode, and any surprises could
OL,17,Fresult in sudden and sharp changes in
OL,18,Fsentiment."
